{"id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MjA5Ng_0005", "text": "別人亦很好 別人亦都很愛我", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 0, 2, 9, 9, 2, 0, 2, 3, 9, 4, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["bit6", "jan4", "jik6", "han2", "hou2", "bit6", "jan4", "jik6", "dou1", "han2", "oi3", "ngo5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "別人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "亦", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "很", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "好", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "別人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "亦", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "都", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "很", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "如果我們不再見", "artists": ["鄭秀文"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2096", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MjA5Ng_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MjA5Ng_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MjA5Ng_0006", "text": "其實暗地 一直怪他不似你", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 4, 2, 3, 2, 4, 3, 3, 5, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["kei4", "sat6", "am3", "dei6", "jat1", "zik6", "gwaai3", "taa1", "bat1", "ci5", "nei5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "其實", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "暗地", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一直", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怪", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "他", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不似", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "如果我們不再見", "artists": ["鄭秀文"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2096", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MjA5Ng_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MjA5Ng_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MjA5Ng_0007", "text": "每晚唉聲嘆氣 夢裏看不見你", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 5, 3, 3, 4, 4, 2, 5, 4, 3, 4, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["mui5", "maan5", "ai1", "sing1", "taan3", "hei3", "mung6", "leoi5", "hon3", "bat1", "gin3", "nei5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "每晚", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "唉聲嘆氣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "夢裏", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "看不見", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "如果我們不再見", "artists": ["鄭秀文"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2096", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MjA5Ng_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MjA5Ng_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MjA5Ng_0008", "text": "如何能 和你就此不相見 有時 還會恨", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 0, 0, 5, 2, 9, 3, 4, 5, 0, 0, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jyu4", "ho4", "nang4", "wo4", "nei5", "zau6", "ci2", "bat1", "gin3", "jau5", "si4", "waan4", "han6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "如何", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "能", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "和", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "就此", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "相見", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有時", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "還會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "恨", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "如果我們不再見", "artists": ["鄭秀文"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2096", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MjA5Ng_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MjA5Ng_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MjA5Ng_0009", "text": "然後我有我生活 然後你再愛別人", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 5, 5, 5, 3, 2, 0, 2, 5, 4, 4, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jin4", "hau6", "ngo5", "jau5", "ngo5", "sang1", "wut6", "jin4", "hau6", "nei5", "zoi3", "oi3", "bit6", "jan4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "然後", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "生活", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "然後", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "再", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "別人", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "如果我們不再見", "artists": ["鄭秀文"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2096", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MjA5Ng_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MjA5Ng_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
